Plat is the same.  Only difference is the fact that someone is spending Real Life (tm) dollars for it.  And the person selling it?  Probably spent Real Life (tm) time getting it.  <br>
<br>
Not all of us can be on EQ all the time to get what we want.  Some will buy plat and think nothing of it, some will mention they did, and some will get flamed for it.<br>
